# UI Principles

Describe HOW pages should behave, not just what to build.

## Collection Page
Prioritize scanning thousands of cards quickly:
- Sticky header + sticky filters
- Virtualized table (TanStack Virtual)
- Fast searching, instant filtering
- Keyboard shortcuts (`/` search, arrows navigate, Enter detail)
- Infinite scrolling, row selection, bulk editing
- Right-click context menus, double-click opens details

## Dashboard
Vercel-style stat cards, large metrics, quick action links.

## General
Every interaction should feel like a native desktop app.
